      • parseAndExecuteCommand

        public void parseAndExecuteCommand()
        Parse and execute the appropriate command based on the args. The general flow looks like this: 1. Parse a set of global options (eg host/port for the admin server) 2. Parse out the command name 3. Pass the global options and any left over parameters to a command handler
